org.apache.tephra.hbase.coprocessor

Class CellSkipFilter

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.hadoop.hbase.filter.Filter
      • org.apache.hadoop.hbase.filter.FilterBase
        • org.apache.tephra.hbase.coprocessor.CellSkipFilter

  • public class CellSkipFilter
extends org.apache.hadoop.hbase.filter.FilterBase
    Filter that encapsulates another Filter. It remembers the last KeyValue for which the underlying filter returned the ReturnCode#NEXT_COL or ReturnCode#INCLUDE_AND_NEXT_COL, so that when filterKeyValue(org.apache.hadoop.hbase.Cell) is called again for the same KeyValue with different version, it returns ReturnCode#NEXT_COL directly without consulting the underlying Filter. Please see TEPHRA-169 for more details.
